PrecisAuthorization for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to enter into a number of real estate transactions with the REGIONAL MUNICIPALITY OF OTTAWA-CARLETON featuring the divestiture of the MacKenzie King Bridge and the Laurier Avenue Bridge in downtown Ottawa, and the conveyance of some 264 hectares of land located throughout the region, together with the works or facilities erected thereon and any necessary easements.
